OL,3,C'Someone who could do such a thing
OL,4,Cdoesn't deserve to live'
OL,6,FThe brother of dismembered Salford
OL,7,Fpensioner Stuart Everett says his
OL,8,Fkiller is "inhumane" and "doesn't
OL,9,Fdeserve to live".
OL,11,FMarcin Majerkiewicz, 42, was jailed
OL,12,Ffor life with a minimum of 34 years
OL,13,Fbehind bars, on Friday 28 March, for
OL,14,Fthe brutal murder of his housemate.
OL,16,FMajerkiewicz bludgeoned the 67-year-
OL,17,Fold with a hammer at the house they
OL,18,Fshared in Winton, Salford in March
OL,19,F2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/17
