OL,3,C'Someone who could do such a thing
OL,4,Cdoesn't deserve to live'
OL,6,FHe then used a hacksaw to dismember
OL,7,Fhis friend before taking the body
OL,8,Fparts in plastic bags on bus journeys
OL,9,Facross Salford and north Manchester to
OL,10,Fdump the evidence.
OL,12,FThe Polish national later pretended to
OL,13,Fbe Mr Everett to throw friends and
OL,14,Ffamily off the trail, using his phone
OL,15,Fand bank cards, as well as sending a
OL,16,Fbirthday card in his name to his
OL,17,Fbrother, after his death.
