OL,3,C'Someone who could do such a thing
OL,4,Cdoesn't deserve to live'
OL,6,FStuart's brother Richard Ziemacki,
OL,7,Ffrom Derby, described his brother as a
OL,8,F"unique" and "real character" who
OL,9,F"everybody loved".
OL,11,FHe said: "He used to love cricket, he
OL,12,Floved music from the 40s and 50s, like
OL,13,FFrankie Martin, and Rat Pack, all
OL,14,Fthose sort of things.
OL,16,F"He was very much a Polish person. He
OL,17,Fspoke exceptionally good Polish, like
OL,18,Fwe all did.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/17
