OL,3,C'Someone who could do such a thing
OL,4,Cdoesn't deserve to live'
OL,6,F"Stuart would come and visit mainly in
OL,7,FMarch for the Cheltenham Racing
OL,8,FFestival because we'd have a flutter
OL,9,Fon the horses and we used to really
OL,10,Fenjoy it and at Christmas, which was a
OL,11,Fvery important time for us because
OL,12,Fthat is when the Polish traditional
OL,13,FChristmas eve dinner took place.
OL,15,F"When my mother and father passed in
OL,16,F1999, me and my wife took on the
OL,17,Ftradition and (Stuart) would come
OL,18,Fevery single year and he would bring
OL,19,Floads of presents for the whole family
OL,20,Fand it was a really special occasion.
OL,26,@yD@OpmyD@Vpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/17
