OL,3,C'Someone who could do such a thing
OL,4,Cdoesn't deserve to live'
OL,6,F"And I think they said remains had
OL,7,Fbeen found on April 4th, but I said
OL,8,F'I've been in touch with him since
OL,9,Fthen' and I so I basically never
OL,10,Fbelieved them."
OL,12,FRichard said the thought of Marcin
OL,13,Fsending him a birthday cards and
OL,14,Ftexting from his brother's phone,
OL,15,Fposing as him was "horrendous".
OL,17,F"He always used to send me cards and
OL,18,Ftext me and you don't really notice
OL,19,Fhow it is phrased or the English."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/17
