OL,3,C'Someone who could do such a thing
OL,4,Cdoesn't deserve to live'
OL,6,FHe continued: "If it wasn't for the
OL,7,Flady police constable (who saw Marcin
OL,8,Fwalking on the road and identified
OL,9,Fbefore his arrest), he may have got
OL,10,Faway with it and that was quite
OL,11,Famazing that that happened and then
OL,12,Fthey got him."
OL,14,F"Everything that came out in the three
OL,15,Fweeks of the trial, day by day,
OL,16,Flistening to what he actually did took
OL,17,Fits toll on our family,. I couldn't
OL,18,Fbelieve what I was seeing or hearing
OL,19,Fand it is still getting to me.
OL,26,@oD@WpmqD@Rpn
