OL,3,C'Someone who could do such a thing
OL,4,Cdoesn't deserve to live'
OL,6,F"It is affecting my life mentally, and
OL,7,Fwork and it's just been a horrendous
OL,8,Ftime."
OL,10,F"What human being can deny doing
OL,11,Fsomething like that?
OL,13,F"When he knew there was no other
OL,14,Fperson that could have possibly done
OL,15,Fit.
OL,17,F"I was shocked by his complete
OL,18,Fdisregard for what the truth was. He
OL,19,Fmust have been living in a fantasy
OL,20,Fland and maybe he was playing out his
OL,21,Ffantasies.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/17
