OL,3,C'Someone who could do such a thing
OL,4,Cdoesn't deserve to live'
OL,6,F"Maybe it was one of those things that
OL,7,Fcaused him to do the horrific things
OL,8,Fthat he did."
OL,10,FThe police have only ever been able to
OL,11,Frecover a third of Stuart's body.
OL,13,F"They haven't uncovered the other two-
OL,14,Fthirds. I'm sure Majerkiewicz knew
OL,15,Fwhere he put the rest of my brother's
OL,16,Fbody.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/17
