OL,3,C'Someone who could do such a thing
OL,4,Cdoesn't deserve to live'
OL,6,F"There may be a time in the next six
OL,7,Fmonths or 12 months or the next couple
OL,8,Fof years where body parts will be
OL,9,Ffound, they will be DNA'd they will be
OL,10,Ftraced back to my brother and
OL,11,Fobviously it all starts again.
OL,13,F"Everything will re-ignite and it will
OL,14,Fhave a horrendous effect again so it's
OL,15,Fa non-ending thing really."
OL,17,F"The lengths he went to, to try and
OL,18,Fdisguise what he had done was quite
OL,19,Fabhorrent."
