OL,6,FRichard is planning to take his
OL,7,Fbrother's remains back to Poland where
OL,8,Fthey both took their parents ashes.
OL,10,F"That's what i'm planning to do later
OL,11,Fon this year, and take him there with
OL,12,Fthe family.
OL,14,F"That may be the end of it, but it
OL,15,Fwon't be will it?"
OL,17,F"He's in prison now, he still knows
OL,18,Fwhere the rest of his body is, but
OL,19,Fwhat I have got of my brother I will
OL,20,Ftreasure."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/17
